728025f-b.title: Queens: Springfield Boulevard - 116th Avenue
728025f-b.text:
Springfield Boulevard, near the S.E. corner of 116th Avenue,
showing an old Hendrickson homestead. There were several
Hendrickson farmhouses in the village of Springfield. The pro-
perty was owned by N. Eromenacher in 1891 and by Florenoe C.
Saitn in 1918.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1925
MAY BE REPRODUCED
2-3) The same, at a later date.
P.L.Sperr  March 9, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
